text: Zhakaas is a 2011 Marathi comedy feature film directed by Ankush Chaudhari. It stars Ankush Chaudhari, Amruta Khanvilkar, Sai Tamhankar and Pooja Sawant in lead roles. == Cast == * Ankush Chaudhari * Amruta Khanvilkar * Sai Tamhankar * Pooja Sawant * Jeetendra Joshi * Pushkar Shrotri * Atul Parchure * Sanjay Khapre * Vikas Samudre * Jaywant Wadkar == References == Category:2010s Marathi-language films Category:Indian films
title: Zhakaas
